<section name="452">
	<p>
		The Trading Post has a small market place in the village square, where half a dozen stalls sell a few goods. Items with no purchase price are not available locally.
	</p>
	<market>
		<header type="armour"/>
		<armour name="leather" bonus="1" buy="50" sell="45"/>
		<armour name="ring mail" bonus="2" sell="90"/>
